  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A simple and casual action shooter: your weapons will automatically aim and shoot!<br></li><li>Dash between bullets and kill your way out of numerous enemies!<br></li><li>Four selectable characters, tens of unique weapons and upgrades!<br></li><li>Non-static builds. You may play as you like on the battlefield!<br></li><li>No need to unlock anything. Your knowledge is your best weapon!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A simple and casual action shooter: your weapons will automatically aim and shoot!<br></li><li>Dash between bullets and kill your way out of numerous enemies!<br></li><li>Four selectable characters, tens of unique weapons and upgrades!<br></li><li>Non-static builds. You may play as you like on the battlefield!<br></li><li>No need to unlock anything. Your knowledge is your best weapon!</li></ul>",
